- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with regular languages and normal forms for terms.
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is also likely as the paper involves combinatorial and algebraic structures.
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper deals with decision procedures for word problems.
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is less likely but still possible as the paper involves semigroups, which are used in game theory.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also less likely but possible as the paper involves the study of information content of words in regular languages.
